WEBVTT

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:01.096
and trying to match the speed
of the car next to you precisely

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:03.816
so you can push a button inside that car.

00:01:03.840 --> 00:01:05.215
If they don't catch the ship

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:07.856
in exactly the right place,
at exactly the right time,

00:01:07.880 --> 00:01:09.896
it could crash into the station.

00:01:09.920 --> 00:01:12.840
And even if they don't die,
they'll lose all the supplies.

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:16.696
PN: And I grabbed the mic
and talked to Houston,

00:01:16.720 --> 00:01:21.016
"Houston, we are ready
to grapple the vehicle."

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:23.256
And I felt my voice was shaking.

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:24.496
I was shaking.

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:27.056
I mean, my heart rate
might have been, I don't know --

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:30.376
